data.eml:eml: Nomenclatural notes in Neotropical Acanthocinini (Coleoptera, Cerambycidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Monné, Miguel A., Machado, Vanessa S. (2009): Nomenclatural notes in Neotropical Acanthocinini (Coleoptera, Cerambycidae). Zootaxa 2204: 67-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.275133
